Package object

Class Summary
FixedMass A fixed object that is not affected by applied forces.
Mass Mass object that moves in response to applied forces.
Muscle This class defines the Muscle object, a spring that is able to generate its own force on the two masses attached its endpoints.
Spring Spring object that exerts forces on its two attached masses according to Hooke's law F=-kx.
